OL,3,CMan who caused death of mum, 39, in
OL,4,Ccrash facing 'lengthy' prison term
OL,6,FA man who caused the death of a 39-
OL,7,Fyear-old mum in a crash on the A19 has
OL,8,Fbeen warned to expect a "lengthy"
OL,9,Fprison sentence.
OL,11,FClaire Laybourne, of Hebburn, South
OL,12,FTyneside, was travelling in a
OL,13,FVolkswagen T-Roc when it collided with
OL,14,Fa Skoda Fabia on the northbound
OL,15,Fcarriageway at about 10:40pm on 5
OL,16,FDecember. She died the next day.
OL,18,FThe driver of the Skoda did not stop
OL,19,Fat the scene on the A19 in Holystone,
OL,20,FNorth Tyneside, and instead fled on
OL,21,Ffoot.
