OL,3,CMan who caused death of mum, 39, in
OL,4,Ccrash facing 'lengthy' prison term
OL,6,FRyan Scott, 28, of Blyth, has now
OL,7,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving, causing serious injury to
OL,9,Fanother female by dangerous driving
OL,10,Fand causing death by driving while
OL,11,Funinsured.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the hearing on Wednesday
OL,14,F(21 January), Judge Penny Moreland
OL,15,Fsaid: "The defendant and those with an
OL,16,Finterest in the case should understand
OL,17,Flengthy and immediate custody is
OL,18,Finevitable."
OL,20,FShe adjourned sentencing until 23
OL,21,FFebruary.
