OL,11,FThe judge told Scott, who appeared via
OL,12,Fvideo link to prison, he should be
OL,13,F"under no illusion" about the outcome
OL,14,Fof the case. He was remanded into
OL,15,Fcustody until the next hearing.
OL,17,FIn a statement released shortly after
OL,18,Fthe tragedy, Ms Laybourne's family
OL,19,Fsaid: "Claire was a beautiful soul
OL,20,Fwhose kindness, warmth, and gentle
OL,21,Fstrength touched everyone she met.
