OL,6,F"She was an extraordinary mother, a
OL,7,Fdevoted partner, a cherished daughter,
OL,8,Fa loving auntie, and a loyal friend.
OL,10,F"Her presence lit up every room, and
OL,11,Fher love held our family together in
OL,12,Fways words can never truly capture.
OL,14,F"Our hearts are broken, and our lives
OL,15,Fhave been changed beyond anything we
OL,16,Fcould have imagined.
OL,18,F"The depth of our grief is matched
OL,19,Fonly by the depth of the love we carry
OL,20,Ffor her. We will miss her beyond what
OL,21,Fwords are able to portray.
